titlestmt.titleproper: Guide to the Service Bureau, Yale University, Records
titlestmt.author: compiled by staff of Manuscripts and Archives

publicationstmt.publisher: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

profiledesc.creation: This finding aid was produced using ArchivesSpace on Friday January 11, 2019 at 08:00

repository.corpname: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

did.abstract: The records consist of correspondence, reports, contracts, inventories, budgets, printed material, ledgers, and building report books concerning the operations of the Yale Service Bureau.

odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 5-F (YRG 5-F), Records documenting operations and administrative services at Yale University.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: The materials are open for research.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Service Bureau, Yale University, Records (RU 165). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The records are arranged by accession.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The records consist of correspondence, reports, contracts, inventories, budgets, printed material, ledgers, and building report books concerning the operations of the Yale Service Bureau.
